BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:344@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260517
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260518
SUMMARY:BWA: APL Wixbledon
DESCRIPTION:APL Wixbledon\n\n🎾 Dust Off Your Rackets: Wixbledon is Back! 🎾\nCalling all aces, net-rushers, and “just here for the atmosphere” players! Our annual Wixbledon Tennis Tournament returns on Sunday, May 17th, and it’s time to find your doubles partner!\nWhether you have a pro serve or you’re just in it for the laughs, come join us for a fun family day out in Clapham South to support our latest school projects. \n📅 THE DETAILS:\n* When: Sunday, May 17th @ 2:30 PM\n* Where: Clapham South\n* Format: Teams of 2 players\n* ⁠\n🏆 CHOOSE YOUR CATEGORY:\nWe have three levels of play depending on your skill (and confidence!):\n🟠 Orange Ball: Beginners/Younger pairs\n🟢 Green Ball: Intermediate/Casual players\n🟡 Yellow Ball: Competitive/Experienced players \nReady to play? Grab a partner and sign up here:\nhttps://ecoledewixevents.bigcartel.com/\nSee you on the courts! 🍓🎾✨\nYour APL Team
CATEGORIES:PTA
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:345@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260521
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260522
SUMMARY:BWA: French & British Wine Tasting Evening
DESCRIPTION:BWA PTA French & British Wine Tasting Evening\n\n🍷✨ Save the Date – An Evening Not to Miss!\nJoin us for a French & British Wine Tasting Evening hosted by your PTA, a perfect chance to unwind, connect, and enjoy a touch of European charm.\nWe’re excited to partner with Spy Wines, an independent London-based merchant known for unique, well-crafted bottles. With 20+ years of experience, they’ll be bringing a fantastic selection for us to enjoy 🍇🥂\n📅 Thursday 21 May\n⏰ From 7:00 PM\n📍 At school\nExpect a relaxed and sociable evening, great company, and plenty of wines to discover.\nMore details to follow soon… mark your calendars! We’d love to see you there!
CATEGORIES:PTA
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:346@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
SUMMARY:BWA: APL Summer Kermesse
DESCRIPTION:APL Summer Kermesse\n\nThe big one! Let’s celebrate the height of summer and the end of the school year together at our annual Kermesse. Expect games, food, and plenty of sunshine as we bring the whole school family together. \nMore details to come!
CATEGORIES:PTA
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:323@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260424
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260425
SUMMARY:BWA: Professional Bike Health Checks
DESCRIPTION:Professional bike health checks available at school as part of Earth Week 2026.\n\nAs part of Earth Week 2026 celebrations, the PTA is joining the APL to host a professional Bike Health Check service at the school. Pricing: 10 GBP for a small bike, 14 GBP for a big bike (24 inches and above). Advance booking is required via the school events portal. Drop off bikes between 8:00 AM and 9:00 AM in front of the school; pick up at the end of the school day from inside the school grounds.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:324@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260423
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260424
SUMMARY:BWA: Deadline -  Notification of student departure for September
DESCRIPTION:Request for parents to inform the school office if their child will not be returning to BWA in September.\n\nMiss Henry, Headteacher, requests that parents inform the school office in writing if their child will not be returning to Belleville Wix Academy in September to assist with planning and class organization. If no notification is received, the school will assume the child is returning.
CATEGORIES:ADMIN
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR